{npm init -y}
this code will install json files

{npm install express body-parser pg bcryptjs ejs}
his will install basic modules for authentification

express → web framework to handle routes (app.get, app.post etc).

body-parser → reads form data (req.body.username, req.body.password).

pg → PostgreSQL client to connect Node.js ↔ PostgreSQL.

bcryptjs → to hash & verify passwords securely.

ejs → template engine (renders HTML with <%= %>).
